---
// Footer.astro
---

<footer class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-400 py-12 border-t border-slate-800">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-8">
      <!-- Brand column -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Triodose Digital" class="h-8 w-auto object-contain flex-shrink-0 brightness-0 invert" style="height: 32px; width: auto;" />
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 max-w-xs">
          川朵數位工作室專注於打造「輕鬆、遊戲化、有溫度」的行動學習與生活工具，致力於透過貼心體驗解決生活真實痛點。
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links column -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">網站導覽</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li>
            <a href="/" class="hover:text-brand-mint transition-colors">首頁</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/products" class="hover:text-brand-mint transition-colors">產品介紹</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-brand-mint transition-colors">隱私權政策</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact column -->
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white tracking-wider uppercase">聯絡我們</h3>
        <p class="text-sm">
          若有任何合作提案或產品反饋，歡迎隨時來信：
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-brand-mint" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 2.25 17.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 19.5 4.5H4.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-1.07-1.916V6.75" />
          </svg>
          <a href="mailto:cs.jian@triodose.com" class="text-sm text-white hover:text-brand-mint transition-colors font-medium">
            cs.jian@triodose.com
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-800 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center text-xs text-slate-500 space-y-4 sm:space-y-0">
      <div>
        &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Triodose Studio. All rights reserved.
      </div>
      <div>
        Created by <span class="text-slate-400 font-medium">C.S. Jian</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
